  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Face coverings: when to wear one, exemptions, and how to make your own
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">This page explains when to wear a face covering, exemptions from wearing one, and how to make your own face covering.</p>

  </div>
</div>

